    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Adults of Sattleria. 1 – 2, S. melalecuella (Constant), 1, 3, 2, Ƥ; 3, S. karsholti sp. nov., 3, holotype; 4, S. cottiella sp. nov., 3, holotype; 5, S. izoardi Huemer & Sattler, 3; 6, S. graiaeella sp. nov., 3, holotype; 7, S. basistrigella Huemer, 3; 8, S. triglavica Povolný, 3." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278323/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278325>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13 – 16. Male genitalia of Sattleria. 13, S. pyrenaica (Petry), slide GEL 279; 14, S. cottiella sp. nov., paratype, slide GEL 1144; 15, S. izoardi Huemer, holotype, slide GEL 1145; 16, S. marguareisi Huemer & Sattler, paratype, slide GEL 150." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278325/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278329>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 31. Male genitalia of Sattleria (details of valva-vinculum complex). 28, S. cottiella sp. nov., paratype, slide GEL 1144; 29, ditto, paratype, slide GEL 1146; 30, S. izoardi Huemer & Sattler, holotype, slide GEL 1145; 31, ditto, slide GEL 1049." ;
